{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I brought-- his name was Gunther-- to the train, and there was a-- a friend of mine, a girlfriend, who came along.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we got to the train, then Gunther said, take my food card, because that way you can stand in line twice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, it was very forbidden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I didn't have any pockets to hide it, and my friend, whose name I will not mention because she also survived, said, I'll carry it for you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a pocket.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, thanks, and I'll come tonight and I'll get it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went there in the evening, she said she lost it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, you couldn't have.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't lose food cards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she says, I lost it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I went to her mother and I said, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So and So, she's lying to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the mother said, you know, she doesn't lie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, I mean, I can swear they had that card.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, that's the kind of thing that hurt me, you know, those kind of experiences.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I remember feelings about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't remember feelings about hunger or anything like that, but I remember feelings around that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's probably of being betrayed by-- from a source that you don't expect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I once got very angry with my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not outwardly-- I was well brought up, and you didn't show this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still don't show emotions too well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She pointed out to me that lots of kids brought potatoes home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, well, you know where they get them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They steal them from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother said, so?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, they steal them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother said, is that so bad?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
